title: ARIES AeroTread™ Install 67" Running Boards on Jeep® Grand Cherokee Bracket 2051139
description:
This video demonstrates the installation of the ARIES 67" AeroTread™ running boards on a 2013 Jeep Grand Cherokee. These running boards are available in a stainless steel or black powder coated aluminum finish.  For this installation, we used the 2051139 bracket. These brackets are vehicle specific.

Features Include:
304 stainless steel front trim  or 201 stainless steel with carbide black powder coat finish
Lightweight, aluminum alloy construction
Full-length plastic tread

(2051139 Bracket) Vehicle Coverage:
2010-2015 Toyota Highlander

Part #
2051139 (Bracket)
2051867 (Stainless steel)
2051967 (Black)
